    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/6454b3e1061d8c63d0ee8423db9d8749.avif?t=1698129561\" width=460 height=214 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【故事介绍】</h2>在和平的葡葡果蜜花园小镇，有一个热心的勇者叫做莱特。他十分喜欢帮助别人，在小镇中过着快乐而自在的生活。<br>直到某天，他的朋友向他道出一个秘密……<br>“莱特，你一定要……”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【玩法介绍】</h2>这是一个轻松可爱的剧情向rpg游戏，玩家将与勇者莱特一起在温馨小镇进行愉快生活！<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你可以与小镇的朋友聊天，探索发现新风景~<br></li><li>帮助居民们完成他们的请求，这是勇者该做的事！<br></li><li>在粉红沙滩钓鱼享受悠闲时光。<br></li><li>烹饪美味食物来送给居民吧。<br></li><li>不过在那之前得先种植作物哦。<br></li><li>对了，再帮镇长做一件新衣服吧！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特的世界观与可爱剧情，内含furry与GB元素，调查发现更多惊喜！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/856baf3bd7442c196d96c6759493ba11.poster.avif?t=1698129561\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/856baf3bd7442c196d96c6759493ba11.webm?t=1698129561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/856baf3bd7442c196d96c6759493ba11.mp4?t=1698129561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>丰富的小游戏和轻松互动，你可以在这里自由探索，完成各种有趣的任务！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/f5445d32801fabba63a289af2db581f0.poster.avif?t=1698129561\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/f5445d32801fabba63a289af2db581f0.webm?t=1698129561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/f5445d32801fabba63a289af2db581f0.mp4?t=1698129561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>清新优美的美术风格，游戏中涵盖大量动画，CG与美丽地图场景哦！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/747d47821440624b9eced19c01c48eb7.poster.avif?t=1698129561\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/747d47821440624b9eced19c01c48eb7.webm?t=1698129561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305480/extras/747d47821440624b9eced19c01c48eb7.mp4?t=1698129561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【关于游玩】</h2><br>「游戏时长」<br>2小时<br><br>「结局数量」<br>2个结局<br>解锁特殊回忆剧情且在游戏内达成2个结局将自动进入附赠房间<br><br>「操作方式」<br>方向键/鼠标：移动<br>Shift+方向键： 跑步<br>空格/鼠标：对话/调查物品（长按空格跳过对话）<br>ESC/鼠标右键：取消/打开菜单<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【staff】</h2>制作人、剧本：lidogegg<br><br>美术：lidogegg、伊柚<br>发行：梦结界工作室<br><br>特别感谢：<br>音乐感谢Alexander Nakarada，更多引用素材来源详见游戏内ED<br>本游戏使用GameCreator开发<br>",
